  "description": "Update a tractor odometer reading.",
  "permissions": "Admins can update. Non-admins can update if the reading has no tractor yet, if they are a member of the broker for the reading, if they are the driver for the driver day, or if they are a manager member of the trucker for the reading.",
  "side_effects": "After commit, updates driver day odometer calculations when value or driver day changes.",
  "validation_notes": "Requires <id> argument (odometer reading ID). At least one attribute or relationship must be provided to update. reading-on must be YYYY-MM-DD when provided. reading-time must be HH:MM or HH:MM:SS when provided. date-sequence must be an integer when provided. value must be numeric and between 0 and 1,000,000. state-code must be a US state abbreviation. unit-of-measure must be one of linear_meter or mile. If driver-day is set, tractor must be on that driver day.",
